UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EGYPT; UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID -- 
EGYPT; EGYPT -- FINANCES; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN POLICY; UNITED STATES -- 
ARMS SALES -- ISRAEL; UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID -- ISRAEL; UNITED STATES -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; HOSTAGES -- IRAQ; AMERICANS -- IRAQ; UNITED STATES 
-- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; GORBACHEV, MIKHAIL S; SUMMIT CONFERENCES; UNITED 
STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EUROPE 
</P>
