Hernandez, LB, 5-10, 175, Jr.; Rob Logoteta, LB, 5-5, 160, Sr.; Lou Morales, 
TB, 5-9, 160, Sr.; Bernie Rivas, OT, 6-0, 210, Sr.; Mike Ryan, FS, 6-2, 180, 
Sr.; Ben Segura, OG, 6-1, 205, Sr. Sean Tracey, OT, 6-0, 200, Sr. 
</P>
