selection, returns to bolster Valencia. Sixth in a series of league previews. ; 
Photo, Valencia linebacker Mike Ehli, a three-year starter and first-team 
all-league selection, typifies the work ethic of his coach. CHRISTINE COTTER / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
