<HEADLINE>
<P>
CORONA DEL MAR VOLLEYBALL PLAYER COMMITS TO USC 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By MIKE REILLEY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Lara Carlsen of Corona del Mar High School has made an oral commitment to play 
volleyball next year at USC. 
</P>
<P>
Carlsen, a 6-foot middle blocker, chose USC over UCLA, Hawaii and the 
University of the Pacific. 
</P>
<P>
