reach the finals of the state tournament. Carlsen is the top returning player 
for the Sea Kings, ranked second in Volleyball Monthly's preseason national 
rankings. 
</P>
<P>
Edison boys' volleyball Coach Brian Rofer, who guided the Chargers to the 
Southern Section 4-A final this past spring, has resigned to accept an 
assistant coaching job at UCLA, his alma mater. Edison officials are seeking a 
replacement. MIKE REILLEY 
